                    <li>Campbell, J. L., Chen, H., Dhaliwal, D. S., Lu, H. M., & Steele, L. B. (2014). The information content of mandatory risk factor disclosures in corporate filings. <em>Review of Accounting Studies</em>, 19(1), 396–455.</li>
